		<title>Lauren Fensterstock’s Cosmic Mosaics Map Out the Unknown in Crystal and Gems</title>
		<link>https://www.sawberries.com/2024/04/29/lauren-fensterstock-mosaic-sculptures/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ross]]></dc:creator>
